<surface xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:mith="http://mith.umd.edu/sc/ns1#" ulx="0"
  uly="0" lrx="5406" lry="7052" xml:id="ox-ms_shelley_e3-0046" partOf="#ox-ms_shelley_e3">
  <graphic url="http://shelleygodwinarchive.org/images/ox/ox-ms_shelley_e3-0046.jp2"/>
  <zone type="main">
    <line>And paved with veined emerald, &amp; a fountain</line>
    <line>Leaps in the mi<mod>
        <del rend="overwritten">r</del>
        <add place="intralinear">d</add>
      </mod>st with an awakening sound;</line>
    <line>From its curved roof the mountain's frozen tears <add><metamark function="count"
          >150</metamark></add></line>
    <line>Like snow or silver or long diamond spires</line>
    <line><milestone unit="tei:seg" spanTo="#e3-0046.05" xml:id="e3-0046.06"/>Hang downward<anchor
        xml:id="e3-0046.05"/>, raining <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">down</del>
        <add place="superlinear">forth</add>
      </mod> a doubtful light; <alt target="#e3-0046.06 #e3-0047.04" mode="excl" weights="1 0"
      /></line>
    <line>And there is heard the ever-moving air</line>
    <line>Whispering without from tree to tree, &amp; birds,</line>
    <line>And bees; and all around are mossy seats</line>
    <milestone unit="tei:l" spanTo="#e3-0046.01"/>
    <line>And the rough walls are clothed with long soft</line>
    <line rend="right">grass</line>
    <anchor xml:id="e3-0046.01"/>
    <line>A simple dwelling, which shall be our own</line>
    <line>Where we will sit &amp; talk of time &amp; change</line>
    <line>As the world ebbs &amp; flows, ourselves unchanged&#8212;</line>
    <line><del rend="strikethrough">For</del> What can hide man from Mutability?&#8212;
          <add><metamark function="count">160</metamark></add></line>
    <line>And <add place="sublinear"><metamark function="insert">^</metamark></add><add
        place="superlinear">if</add> ye sigh, then I will smile, &amp; thou</line>
    <line>Ione, shall chant fragments of sea-music <unclear reason="illegible">,</unclear></line>
    <line>Until I weep, when ye shall smile away</line>
    <milestone unit="tei:l" spanTo="#e3-0046.02"/>
    <line>The tears she brought, which yet were sweet to</line>
    <line rend="right">shed;</line>
    <anchor xml:id="e3-0046.02"/>
    <line>We will entangle buds &amp; flowers,<add place="superlinear"><metamark
          function="displacement">&#x2014;&#x2014;</metamark></add>
      <milestone unit="tei:seg" spanTo="#e3-0046.03" corresp="#e3-0047.01"/>&amp; make<anchor
        xml:id="e3-0046.03"/><anchor xml:id="e3-0046.04"/></line>
    <line>Strange combinations out of common things</line>
    <line>Like human babes in their brief innocence</line>
    <line>And we will search, with looks &amp; words of love</line>
    <line rend="left"><add><metamark function="count">161</metamark></add></line>
  </zone>
</surface>
